	<h1>Penney's Game</h1>
      </div><!-- /header -->
      
      <div data-role="content">	
	
	<p>
	  In this game, you choose a head/tail sequence of length 3, such as HTH, and then let your opponent choose 
	  her head/tail sequence.
	</p>
	<p>
	  A fair coin is then tossed generating a random head/tail sequence until either your sequence or your opponent's 
	  sequence appears.  The player whose sequence appears first wins.
	</p>
	
	
      </div><!-- /content -->
	
